[/size][size=4]

[/size][size=4]
[/size][size=4]
[/size][size=4]I have tested the navmesh with a follower and encountered no problems.[/size][size=4]

[/size][size=4]
[/size][size=4]
[/size][size=6][color=#ff7700]Installation:[/color] [/size][size=4]          Just download with Nexus mod manger, Mod organizer or manual,if you want to install it manually, [/size][size=4]                                                                                             then you have to extract it into your data file for Skyrim.[/size][size=4]
[/size][size=4]
[/size][size=6][color=#ff7700]Unistallation:[/color] [/size][size=4]      Just untick in mod manger or mod organzier or delete the files you manually installed.[/size][size=4]
